ttp_template:
<group name="mode">
  Mode: {{MODE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="interface_status_role">
  {{INTERFACE}} {{STATUS | ORPHRASE}} {{ROLE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
High Availability Status:
  Mode: Active-Standby
  Local Priority: 100
  Remote Priority: 80
  Local State: Active
  Remote State: Standby
  Preemption: Enabled
  Uptime: 2d 4h 15m

  Interface     Status    Role
  eth1          Up        Active
  eth2          Up        Standby
  eth3          Down      Unknown
textfsm_template:
Value MODE (\w+[-]?\w+)
Value LOCAL_PRIORITY (\d+)
Value REMOTE_PRIORITY (\d+)
Value LOCAL_STATE (\w+)
Value REMOTE_STATE (\w+)
Value PREEMPTION (\w+)
Value UPTIME (\d+d \d+h \d+m)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value STATUS (Up|Down)
Value ROLE (\w+)

Start
  ^\s*High Availability Status:$$
  ^\s*Mode:\s+${MODE}$$
  ^\s*Local Priority:\s+${LOCAL_PRIORITY}$$
  ^\s*Remote Priority:\s+${REMOTE_PRIORITY}$$
  ^\s*Local State:\s+${LOCAL_STATE}$$
  ^\s*Remote State:\s+${REMOTE_STATE}$$
  ^\s*Preemption:\s+${PREEMPTION}$$
  ^\s*Uptime:\s+${UPTIME}$$
  ^\s*$$
  ^\s*Interface\s+Status\s+Role$$
  ^\s*${INTERFACE}\s+${STATUS}\s+${ROLE}$$ -> Record
